\subsection{Class template \ccFont Min\_circle\_2\_adapterH2<PT,DA>}

First, we declare the class templates \ccc{Min_circle_2},
\ccc{Min_circle_2_adapterH2} and
\ccc{_Min_circle_2_adapterH2__Circle}.

